name: Pair_compareToTest
description: Unit tests for the compareTo method of the Pair class.

test_cases.name: testCompareTo_DifferentLeft
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the left elements of the pairs are different.

test_cases.name: testCompareTo_SameLeftDifferentRight
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the left elements are the same but the right elements are different.

test_cases.name: testCompareTo_SameLeftSameRight
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when both the left and right elements of the pairs are the same.
